        <item>
            <title>调位事件苦主回港后收到 HK Express 道歉　「但快运仍未就事件作合理解释」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 08:00:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Hk Express]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港快运]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251783</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近航空公司香港快运（HK Express）的强行调位事件引起热议，事缘有两名家长连同两名子女在香港快运前往日本的航班上，强行要求已付费拣位的乘客让出座位，而航空公司仅是向被抢座位乘客表示可以回港后申请退款，处理手法令一众网民不满。事件的最新消息为被抢座位的郑氏夫妇回港后已得到香港快运联络致歉，但表示仍未得到事件的有关合理解释。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251787 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/unwire-1721626780-694x544.jpg" alt="HK Express" width="694" height="544" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/unwire-1721626780-694x544.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/unwire-1721626780.jpg 1147w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=10160062787418144&amp;set=g.638762621229829">HK Express 香港快运及旅行资讯关注组</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">香港快运事后作出的回应，指该一家四口最初预订的座位因机型不同的关系变成了紧急出口座位排，而其中两名乘客因未成年不能坐在紧急出口座位排，与另一排四名乘客（包括已付费拣位的两位乘客）的协商后安排调位。然而郑氏夫妇表示从头到尾都没有与他们协商过就被强行调位，直指香港快运讲大话。香港快运在郑氏夫妇回港后立即进行联络并致歉，指早前与员工的沟通不足，导致作出了不实的回应。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">郑氏夫妇得到了快运的道歉后，表示目前快运仍然未有就事件作出合理的解释，希望快运可以尽快展开调查，要求快运作正式的书面道歉并向公众交代事件的合理解释。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20240722/1721613308139/hk-express%e7%88%ad%e4%bd%8d-%e7%95%b6%e4%ba%8b%e4%ba%ba%e9%84%ad%e6%b0%8f-%e5%9b%9e%e6%b8%af%e5%be%8c%e5%b7%b2%e7%8d%b2%e5%bf%ab%e9%81%8b%e8%81%af%e7%b5%a1%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89-%e6%83%9f%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e4%bb%8d%e6%9c%aa%e6%9c%89%e5%90%88%e7%90%86%e8%a7%a3%e9%87%8b?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2NvUGY0PXZKK2vVcrspHc5NoHX4SHvK8U-03BLf_gRsI1vq9WUcHcZb8c_aem_b9mLYcu8t2Ab9MQn3f7sjw">明报</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1670182-20221008.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/hk-express-2/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">HK Express 新 4 级行李制改逐件计　网民：加钱都解决不了问题</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/">调位事件苦主回港后收到 HK Express 道歉　「但快运仍未就事件作合理解释」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>ZEEKR 009 最豪 MPV 右軚版登场　首创健康减压模式 + 大量内外高科技元素</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/zeekr-009-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=zeekr-009-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/zeekr-009-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 08:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr 009]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[纯电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250814</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ZEEKR 早前宣布正式登陆香港，今日公布豪华旗舰 MPV 全新 ZEEKR 009，其左軚和右軚版本全球同步发售。 香港一换一补贴售价为 $750,000 起。 即日起正式公开接受预订。ZEEKR CEO 在发布会上表示，今年 6 月 ZEEKR 品牌单月交付首度突破 20,000 台；今年上半年，ZEEKR 品牌累计交付超过 87,800 台，在售价 20 万元以上中国纯电品牌中排名第一。 </p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ZEEKR 009 豪华 MPV 车身采用流线型设计，搭配精致的前后灯组，整体造型富有现代感。全系共有 5 种外观颜色，3 种轮圈造型供用户选择，满足不同用户的个性需求。ZEEKR 009 全系升级搭载高性能碳化矽电驱系统，双摩打四驱版本马力达 603 匹，0-100km/h 加速仅需 4.6 秒，比肩高性超跑。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251793" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251829" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-11-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-11-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle24-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle24-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle24-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲车身采用流线型设计</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/launcheventpics4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/launcheventpics4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/launcheventpics4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全系共有 5 种外观颜色，3 种轮圈造型供用户选择</p><p>先从内笼设计讲起，全新 ZEEKR 009 提供 4 种内饰风格，座椅采用 NAPPA 头层真皮和梦幻回弹海绵，座椅整体宽度达到 0.7 米，支援最多 16 项调节，头枕音响、加热、通风和按摩等功能应有尽有。后排座椅更配备了 Eames Chair 模式，靠背可调至 132 度，坐垫前部可升高 20 毫米，腿托可抬升至 90 度，与前排座椅背后的脚踏组成完整平面，能完全伸展双脚，缓解旅途疲劳。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251814" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits15-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits15-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits15-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头枕设有音响</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251812" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits18-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits18-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits18-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲座椅采用梦幻回弹海绵，支援最多 16 项调节</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134514-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134514-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134514.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲后排座椅配备 Eames Chair 模式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134456-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134456-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134456.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134548-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134548-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134548.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲座椅采用 NAPPA 头层真皮</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle23-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle23-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle23-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲靠背可调至 132 度，坐垫前部可升高 20 毫米，腿托可抬升至 90 度</p><p>中控台和娱乐系统方面，前排配备了 15 吋中控大萤幕，后排则配备了 17 吋娱乐大萤幕，皆采用最新 iPad Pro 同款双层 OLED 屏幕。另设有恒温冰箱，制冷最低零下 6°C，制热最高 50°C，支援 24 小时离车工作，并同时亦可用手机 App 控制，还带有紫外线杀菌功能，可放心保存药品和婴儿食品。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle22-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle22-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle22-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前排配备了 15 吋中控大萤幕，采用 iPad Pro 同款双层 OLED 萤幕</p><p>ZEEKR 009 配备多种高科技系统，全系标准配置两颗完全独立的 8295 座舱晶元，据厂商称能够满足至少未来 5 年的座舱算力需求，保护整车隐私安全。ZEEKR 009 亦加入了 KR AI 大模型，将 ZEEKR 智能语音助手 EVA 全面升级为 AI EVA，例如进入隧道时会主动建议关闭车窗打开内回圈，回家停车时会基于通勤习惯提前预测第二天的电量，并主动提醒及时充电。ZEEKR 009 系统内置 ZEEKR 「极拓 APP」，可下载只能在手机上使用的应用程式。 ZEEKR 09 亦预装腾讯会议 Rooms，为商务用家提供方便安全的视像会议体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251825 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-8-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-8-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-8-scaled.jpg 1201w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-35-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-35-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-35.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251827" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-20-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-20-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-20.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251828" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-14-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-14-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-14.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251804" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle28-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle28-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle28-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><p>行车安全系统方面，全新 ZEEKR 009 拥有全方位安全警报系统，以及守护用户隐私的极致安全。ZEEKR 009 的汽车安全资料库通过最严苛的测试验证安全，规模是行业平均水准的 5 倍。ZEEKR 009 配备前双摇臂 + 后集成式多连杆的独立悬挂，全系标准配备 CCD 电磁减振，并升级了双腔空气悬架。ZEEKR 009 满足「母婴级」使用标准，同时通过了中汽中心儿童绿色座舱认证以及中环联合认证中心生态纺织品认证。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle211-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle211-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle211-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits33-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits33-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits33-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ZEEKR 009 标配 ZEEKR 首创的「健康减压舱」功能，在「休憩」和「治愈」模式之外，首次推出「冥想模式」，内置 8 套不同场景的冥想课程，智能联动音乐、灯光、萤幕和座椅振子，让乘客进入身心放松的境界。 此外亦加入了「足底养生」，在第二排座椅的脚踏上，加入了可独立控制的足底加热功能，温度 3 档可调。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251823" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722141950-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722141950-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722141950.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲第二排座椅的脚踏上加入可独立控制的足底加热功能</p><h2>规格（<strong><b> </b></strong>6 座行政版及 7 座中通道版）</h2><table><tbody><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>摩打类别</b></strong><strong><b> </b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>高性能永磁同步电驱动系统：双电机</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>电池容量</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>116 kWh</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>最大马力</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>603hp </p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>最大扭力</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>693 Nm</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>0–100 km/h</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>4.6 s</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>续航力</b></strong><strong><b> （WLTP）</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>580 km</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>最大充电功率</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>150 kW （DC）</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><b>香港一换一补贴售价</b></strong></p></td><td><p>港币 $750,000 起</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>ZEEKR Space：<br />地址： 香港湾仔告士打道 39 号夏悫大厦地下 A 舖<br />服务时间： 星期一至日及公众假期，上午 9 时正至晚上 8 时正</p><p>ZEEKR Gallery：<br />地址： 香港太古城太古湾道 12 号地下<br />服务时间： 星期一至日及公众假期，上午 9 时正至晚上 8 时正</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/zeekr-x/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">ZEEKR X 右軚版本登场，四驱版马力达 428 匹</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/17/%e6%a5%b5%e6%b0%aa-zeekr-x-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%a9%a6%e9%a7%95-b-%e6%9f%b1%e5%89%b5%e6%84%8f%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e8%bb%8a%e4%b8%bb%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">极氪 Zeekr X 香港试驾 : B 柱创意科技宠物车主最爱</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/zeekr-x-rhd-hong-kong-macau/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Zeekr X 右軚版本投产，香港澳门或成全球首发市场</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/zeekr-009-2/life-tech/auto/">ZEEKR 009 最豪 MPV 右軚版登场　首创健康减压模式 + 大量内外高科技元素</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
